text.tspan: ECI ranking vs. GDP per capita, 2015
The ECI ranking orders countries from the most to the least economically complex. GDP per capita is adjusted for
inflation (at 2011 international prices) and accounts for the differences in purchasing power.
OEC ECI Ranking (Observatory of Economic Complexity (2016))
Source: ECI - Observatory of Economic Complexity (OEC) (2016) and the Atlas of Economic Complexity (2016), GDP per capita PPP 2011 – WDI
